{
    "id": "adaptive-metrics-auto-apply",
    "title": "Enable auto-apply recommendations",
    "blocks": [{
            "type": "markdown",
            "content": "# Enable auto-apply recommendations\n\nWhen you are comfortable with the recommendations and have protected critical metrics with exemptions, you can enable auto-apply for a fully automated workflow.\n\nOnce enabled, the system automatically applies new optimization recommendations as they are generated."
        },
        {
            "type": "multistep",
            "content": "Navigate to **Adaptive Metrics** > **Configuration**.",
            "requirements": ["navmenu-open"],
            "steps": [{
                    "action": "highlight",
                    "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/a/grafana-adaptive-metrics-app/overview']",
                    "tooltip": "Click Adaptive Metrics"
                },
                {
                    "action": "highlight",
                    "reftarget": "a[data-testid='data-testid Nav menu item'][href='/a/grafana-adaptive-metrics-app/configuration']",
                    "tooltip": "Click Configuration"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "markdown",
            "content": "Click the **Edit** icon next to the segment you want to enable auto-apply for (default or existing segment)."
        },
        {
            "type": "markdown",
            "content": "Select the **Enable auto-apply** checkbox."
        },
        {
            "type": "markdown",
            "content": "Click **Save** to apply the changes."
        }
    ]
}